==Polish==
===Noun===
'''polski''' {{m}} {{s}} ''declines as adjective''; also '''język polski''' {{m}} {{s}} ''[[inanimate]]''.
# [[language]] of [[Poland]]; "''po polsku''" "in Polish," "''z (języka) polskiego''", "from Polish," "''na (język) polski''" "into Polish."

===Adjective===
'''polski''' ''masculine singular nominative''
# of, or from [[Poland]]
